com.unvired.sync.in
Interface IConflictHandler

public interface IConflictHandler

Conflict handler to handle the conflict between the data in the mobile application and the incoming data from the server. Application has to implement this interface to handle the conflicts.

Method Summary
 void handleConflict(java.util.Vector<ConflictBE> conflictBEs)
          Handle the conflict between the existing data structure and the incoming data structure.
 

Method Detail

handleConflict

void handleConflict(java.util.Vector<ConflictBE> conflictBEs)
Handle the conflict between the existing data structure and the incoming data structure. For the existing data only the header is passed. For the incoming data both the headers and items are provided. In the current model conflicts are not checked at a structure level but at a BE level. So any change in the header or items of the mobile application is marked as change in the header.

Parameters:
conflictBEs - - Existing header data structure in the application that is changed and has a conflict with the incoming data.
